1511.title: Robin

15111.content:
Robin knocked on Starfire's door.

"Come in"

"Hey Starfire, I was just looking at your Earth files"

"My what?"

"You know, the files about you coming from Tamran to Earth, the um.... T.O.E... yah!"

"That spells toe"

"Never mind that, I found something I think you should hear. Since you have not lived your whole life on this planet you do not have a record. You are going to have to start over"

"What do you mean starting of the over"

"You have no record so we are going to have to make you one. Otherwise, T.O.E is going to have to kick you off of Earth!"

"Oh no! Please friend Robin! Help me get the record for I do not want to leave Earth!"

"All right then, just listen to me and everything will be fine. It is time for the first step!"
15111.title: Plan 1

151111.content:
Starfire was sitting on her bed petting Silkie.

"All right Star, lie down on the bed" Star put Silkie on the floor and lay on the bed. Robin removed Star's boots and skirt and put them on the side.

"Robin what are you doing?" Star said, quickly covering herself

"Star this is the first step, I am diapering you" Robin moved her arms and removed Star's underwear and grabbed a puffy diaper "lift up your butt" Robin put the diaper under and taped it around Star's waist.

"Robin is this truly necessary?"

"Yes it is. Babies have accidents all the time"

"But i am not the baby"

"Yes you are. that is what restart means now follow me"
